data.description: Vacant and ready to move in !! Beautiful two story 3 bedrooms, 2 and half bath home located in Southwest San Antonio. Enjoy active living with easy access to community trails, pool, and park. this gorgeous home features granite countertops, beautiful tile floors in all living areas, 3 spacious bedrooms with walk-in closets, and a two car garage. Plenty of storage space for the whole family, open living areas. Roomy master bedroom with oversized walk in closet.  Minutest from the Joint Base San Antonio (Lackland), Texas A&M University, shopping, grocery stores, & downtown San Antonio. This open concept home inspires family gatherings and holiday entertaining. Won't last long. Make an appointment today !
